line: You know high school is a really turbulent time in a lot of peoples lives.

name: Monika
line: People can get really passionate and dramatic.

name: Monika
line: And others have aching hearts and seek attention on social media...

name: Monika
line: But all of the social pressure and hormones can lead to a dark time in peoples lives.

name: Monika
line: Everyone has a story.

name: Monika
line: You may not know what someone is really feeling on the inside.

name: Monika
line: Many people who are depressed wont even bother telling the world about it.

name: Monika
line: They dont want attention because theyve already given up on the inside.

name: Monika
line: Their feeling of worthlessness is so overwhelming that they dont even want people to tell them otherwise.

name: Monika
line: Depression comes in many forms but that is one of them.

name: Monika
line: Just if you think you know someone struggling with depression...

name: Monika
line: You can help just by treating them like theyre a good friend.

name: Monika
line: Spend time with them even if they dont feel like doing much.

name: Monika
line: And remind them that they always have something to look forward to.

name: Monika
line: Making plans in advance letting them borrow something or even just saying See you at school tomorrow...

name: Monika
line: All of those things can help your friend make it to the next day.

name: Monika
line: I hope being friends with Sayori has given you some perspective on the true face of depression.

name: Monika
line: Yeah shes gone now...

name: Monika
line: But Sayori was never real in the first place.

name: Monika
line: Youre real.

name: Monika
line: Your friends are real.

name: Monika
line: And just by being a good person you can save someones life.

name: Monika
line: As for you...

name: Monika
line: ...You dont struggle with depression or anything like that do you?

name: Monika
line: Because you too have people who would want to save your life.

name: Monika
line: Maybe they dont express it every day or maybe they dont even know how to.

name: Monika
line: But people do feel that way.

name: Monika
line: I promise.

name: Monika
line: ...Man humans are complicated!

name: Monika
line: But as long as youre here with me Ill take care of you my love.

name: Monika
line: Do you ever just feel like theres no real reason for you to be alive?

name: Monika
line: I dont mean in like a suicidal way.

name: Monika
line: I just mean how nothing that we do is special.

name: Monika
line: Just being in school or working at some job for some company.

name: Monika
line: Its like youre completely replaceable and the world wouldnt miss you if you were gone.

name: Monika
line: It makes me really want to go and change the world after I graduate.

name: Monika
line: But the older I get the more I realize that its an immature frame of thinking.

name: Monika
line: Its not like I can just go change the world.

name: Monika
line: Like what are the chances that Ill be the one to invent artificial intelligence or become President?

name: Monika
line: It feels like Im never going to make up for the heaps of resources Ive spent living my life.

name: Monika
line: Thats why I think the key to happiness is to just be hopelessly selfish.

name: Monika
line: Just to look out for oneself and those who happen to be their friends only because they grew up with them.

name: Monika
line: Never mind the fact that theyre spending their entire life taking and consuming and never giving back.

name: Monika
line: But when people realize the world would benefit more from them killing themselves they change their whole philosophy!

name: Monika
line: Its like they have to justify their reason to live by tricking themselves into thinking theyre doing good.

name: Monika
line: Anyway I want to live my life desperately striving to pay back my lifetimes worth of consumption.

name: Monika
line: If I ever surpass that point then Im a net positive and I can die happy.

name: Monika
line: Of course even if I fail to do that...

name: Monika
line: I think I would be too selfish to kill myself anyway.

name: Monika
line: So much for being a good person right?

line: Ahaha!

name: Monika

name: Monika
line: Well I guess a lot of people are more concerned about it being inhumane and all that...

name: Monika

name: Monika

name: Monika
line: And of course we all kill billions of microorganisms daily without even giving it thought.

name: Monika

name: Monika
line: I mean what if plants feel some kind of pain too and we just dont understand it?

name: Monika
line: What if pulling leaves off a stem feels like someone ripping off your fingers one by one?

name: Monika

name: Monika
line: Anyway if you ever feel like making a small contribution to the planet it doesnt hurt to choose veggies once in a while!

line: I mean a lot of people say that they only write for themselves...

name: Monika
line: But I think its hard to say its just as fulfilling as when you share with people.

name: Monika
line: Even if it takes time to find the right people to share with.

name: Monika

name: Monika
line: Were programmed to desire social feedback.

name: Monika

name: Monika
line: Thats why life can be so confusing for introverts.

name: Monika
line: Being an introvert doesnt mean you shun social interaction and hate being around people.

name: Monika
line: It means social interaction especially in groups or unfamiliar places uses up a lot of energy.

name: Monika
line: Like a lot of introverts sit at home and feel lonely and restless...

name: Monika
line: ...And then when they finally go out after a half hour they just want to go home again.

name: Monika
line: I think if more people could understand how it works they would respect it a lot more.

name: Monika
line: Many introverts do enjoy having people around.

name: Monika
line: They love just having one or two close friends over and just leisurely hanging out.

name: Monika
line: Even if youre not actively spending time together it feels nice for them just to have you there.

name: Monika

line: But you have all these students who have no idea what they want to do with their life...

name: Monika
line: And instead of taking the time to figure it out they go to college for business or communication or psychology.

name: Monika
line: Not because they have an interest in those fields...

name: Monika
line: ...but because they just hope the degree will get them some kind of job after college.

name: Monika
line: So the end result is that there are fewer jobs to go around for those entry-level degrees right?

name: Monika
line: So the basic job requirements get higher which forces even more people to go to college.

name: Monika
line: And colleges are also businesses so they just keep raising their prices due to the demand...

name: Monika
line: ...So now we have all these young adults tens of thousands of dollars in debt with no job.

name: Monika
line: But despite all that the routine stays the same.

name: Monika

line: I can enjoy horror novels but not really horror movies.

name: Monika
line: The problem I have with horror movies is that most of them just rely on easy tactics.

name: Monika
line: Like dark lighting and scary-looking monsters and jump scares and things like that.

name: Monika
line: Its not fun or inspiring to get scared by stuff that just takes advantage of human instinct.

name: Monika
line: But with novels its a little different.

name: Monika
line: The story and writing need to be descriptive enough to put genuinely disturbing thoughts into the readers head.

name: Monika
line: It really needs to etch them deeply into the story and characters and just mess with your mind.

name: Monika
line: In my opinion theres nothing more creepy than things just being slightly off.

name: Monika
line: Like if you set up a bunch of expectations on what the story is going to be about...

name: Monika
line: ...And then you just start inverting things and pulling the pieces apart.

name: Monika
line: So even though the story doesnt feel like its trying to be scary the reader feels really deeply unsettled.

name: Monika
line: Like they know that something horribly wrong is hiding beneath the cracks just waiting to surface.

name: Monika
line: God just thinking about it gives me the chills.

name: Monika
line: Heres Monikas Writing Tip of the Day!

name: Monika
line: Sometimes when I talk to people who are impressed by my writing they say things like I could never do that.

name: Monika
line: Its really depressing you know?

name: Monika
line: As someone who loves more than anything else to share the joy of exploring your passions...

name: Monika
line: ...it pains me when people think that being good just comes naturally.

name: Monika
line: Thats how it is with everything not just writing.

name: Monika
line: When you try something for the first time youre probably going to suck at it.

name: Monika
line: Sometimes when you finish you feel really proud of it and even want to share it with everyone.

name: Monika
line: But maybe after a few weeks you come back to it and you realize it was never really any good.

name: Monika
line: That happens to me all the time.

name: Monika
line: It can be pretty disheartening to put so much time and effort into something and then you realize it sucks.

name: Monika
line: But that tends to happen when youre always comparing yourself to the top professionals.

name: Monika
line: When you reach right for the stars theyre always gonna be out of your reach you know?

name: Monika
line: The truth is you have to climb up there step by step.

name: Monika
line: And whenever you reach a milestone first you look back and see how far youve gotten...

name: Monika
line: And then you look ahead and realize how much more there is to go.

name: Monika
line: So sometimes it can help to set the bar a little lower...

name: Monika
line: Try to find something you think is ipretty/i good but not world-class.

name: Monika
line: And you can make that your own personal goal.

name: Monika
line: Its also really important to understand the scope of what youre trying to do.

name: Monika
line: If you jump right into a huge project and youre still amateur youll never get it done.

name: Monika
line: So if were talking about writing a novel might be too much at first.

name: Monika
line: Why not try some short stories?

name: Monika
line: The great thing about short stories is that you can focus on just one thing that you want to do right.

name: Monika
line: That goes for small projects in general - you can really focus on the one or two things.

name: Monika
line: Its such a good learning experience and stepping stone.

name: Monika
line: Oh one more thing...

name: Monika
line: Writing isnt something where you just reach into your heart and something beautiful comes out.

name: Monika
line: Just like drawing and painting its a skill in itself to learn how to express what you have inside.

name: Monika
line: That means there are methods and guides and basics to it!

name: Monika
line: Reading up on that stuff can be super eye-opening.

name: Monika
line: That sort of planning and organization will really help prevent you from getting overwhelmed and giving up.

name: Monika
line: And before you know it...

name: Monika
line: You start sucking less and less.

name: Monika
line: Nothing comes naturally.

name: Monika
line: Our society our art everything - its built on thousands of years of human innovation.

name: Monika
line: So as long as you start on that foundation and take it step by step...

name: Monika
line: You too can do amazing things.

name: Monika
line: ...Thats my advice for today!

name: Monika
line: Thanks for listening~

line: Back in my debate club days I learned a whole lot about arguing...

name: Monika
line: The problem with arguing is that each person sees their opinion as the superior one.

name: Monika
line: Thats kind of stating the obvious but it affects the way they try to get their point across.

name: Monika
line: Lets say you really like a certain movie right?

name: Monika
line: If someone comes along and tells you the movie sucks because it did X and Y wrong...

name: Monika
line: Doesnt that make you feel kind of personally attacked?

name: Monika
line: Its because by saying that its like theyre implying that you have bad taste.

name: Monika
line: And once emotions enter the picture its almost guaranteed that both people will be left sour.

name: Monika
line: But its all about language!

name: Monika
line: If you make everything as subjective-sounding as possible then people will listen to you without feeling attacked.

name: Monika
line: You could say Im personally not a fan of it and I felt that Id like it more if it did X and Y...things like that.

name: Monika
line: It even works when youre citing facts about things.

name: Monika
line: If you say I read on this website that it works like this...

name: Monika
line: Or if you admit that youre not an expert on it...

name: Monika
line: Then its much more like youre putting your knowledge on the table rather than forcing it onto them.

name: Monika
line: If you put in an active effort to keep the discussion mutual and level they usually follow suit.

name: Monika
line: Then you can share your opinions without anyone getting upset just from a disagreement.

name: Monika
line: Plus people will start seeing you as open-minded and a good listener!

name: Monika
line: Its a win-win you know?

name: Monika
line: ...Well I guess that would be Monikas Debate Tip of the Day!

name: Monika
line: Do you ever feel like you waste too much time on the internet?

name: Monika
line: Social media can practically be like a prison.

name: Monika
line: Its like whenever you have a few seconds of spare time you want to check on your favorite websites...

name: Monika
line: And before you know it hours have gone by and youve gotten nothing out of it.

name: Monika
line: Anyway its really easy to blame yourself for being lazy...

name: Monika
line: But its not really even your fault.

name: Monika
line: Addiction isnt usually something you can just make disappear with your own willpower.

name: Monika
line: You have to learn techniques to avoid it and try different things.

name: Monika
line: For example there are apps that let you block websites for intervals of time...

name: Monika
line: Or you can set a timer to have a more concrete reminder of when its time to work versus play...

name: Monika
line: Or you can separate your work and play environments which helps your brain get into the right mode.

name: Monika
line: Even if you make a new user account on your computer to use for work thats enough to help.

name: Monika
line: Putting any kind of wedge like that between you and your bad habits will help you stay away.

name: Monika
line: Just remember not to blame yourself too hard if youre having trouble.

name: Monika
line: If its really impacting your life then you should take it seriously.
